,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":24940,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/hadith-on-hygiene-clean-your-nose-three-times-in-the-morning\/","url_meta":{"origin":15423,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Hygiene: Clean your nose three times in the morning","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you awakens from his sleep, then let him perform ablution and sniff water into his nose three times. Verily, Satan spends the night in the upper part of his nose.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3121, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2787,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/06\/wudu-perfect-ablution\/","url_meta":{"origin":15423,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Description of a perfect ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Humran reported: Uthman, may Allah be pleased with him, requested a vessel of water and he poured water over his hands three times and washed them. Then, he put his right hand in the vessel and rinsed his mouth and sniffed water into his nose. Then, he washed his face\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/12\/believer-or-merely-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":15423,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Or maybe he is merely a Muslim?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was distributing charity, so I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, give it to this man for he is a believer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cOr merely a Muslim.\u201d I said it three times and the Prophet repeated it three\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25511,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/01\/taharah-purity-wash-hands-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":15423,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Taharah: Wash hands on waking up, before ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 1, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you awakens from sleep, do not let him dip his hands into the vessel until he washes them three times. Verily, he does not know where his hand spent the night.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 160,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35734,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/22\/wudu-3-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":15423,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Washing limbs three times in ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 22, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how does one perform purification?\u201d The Prophet called for a vessel of water, then he washed his hands three times, then he washed his face three times,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34663,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/07\/prophet-dua-three-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":15423,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet supplicates and asks three times","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 7, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when he would supplicate, he would supplicate three times, and when he would ask Allah, he would ask three times. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1794 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15423","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\